    """Check 15: the canonical hard-stop / token-Notbremse thresholds appear VERBATIM in build-loop.md §6
    as exact operator-anchored strings (build-gates §6 check 15) — so the autonomous loop cannot silently
    run on stale/fuzzy thresholds (read "~8" as 5 or 15). Target-absent until build-loop.md exists
    (P0.6-authored); fail-closed once present (P0.6.7-activated)."""
